title: A small little youtube channel
body:
Hey Summoners!
My summoner name is Kuaisu and I have a small and growing channel! I would really hope you will all visit my channel and watch a few of my videos. You can choose to or not but support would be very much appreciated. 
Thank you for reading this,
Kuaisu (Oceania)
